<div class="panel">
	<h3><i class="icon icon-credit-card"></i> {l s='CoolPay' mod='coolpay'}</h3>
	<p>
		<strong>{l s='This module allows you to accept payments using CoolPay.' mod='coolpay'}</strong>
	</p>
	<p>
		{l s='In order for the module to work, you need to configure merchant ID, agreement ID, API key and private key.' mod='coolpay'}
		{l s='These values can be found in the CoolPay control panel in the Settings tree.' mod='coolpay'}
	</p>
	<p>
		{l s='The user key must be configured in order to capture, cancel and refund transactions via the API. The user key is also used to calculate the fees if you let the customer pay the fees. For safety reasons it is recommended to create a user with minimal access rights.' mod='coolpay'}
	</p>
	<p>
		{l s='Notice that you may change the ordering of the cards with drag/drop.' mod='coolpay' mod='coolpay'}
	</p>
</div>